{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 生物信息学数据可视化实验\n",
    "\n",
    "本实验将学习如何使用Python进行生物信息学数据的可视化。\n",
    "\n",
    "## 实验目标\n",
    "- 掌握常用的生物信息学可视化方法\n",
    "- 学会创建热图、PCA图、聚类图\n",
    "- 理解数据可视化的最佳实践\n",
    "- 学会使用matplotlib和seaborn"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "from scipy.cluster.hierarchy import dendrogram, linkage\n",
    "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler\n",
    "from sklearn.decomposition import PCA\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei']\n",
    "plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"库导入成功\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 准备数据"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "data = {\n",
    "    'Sample': ['S1', 'S2', 'S3', 'S4', 'S5', 'S6'],\n",
    "    'Gene1': [10.5, 11.2, 15.3, 16.1, 9.8, 10.5],\n",
    "    'Gene2': [8.2, 7.9, 14.2, 13.8, 8.0, 8.2],\n",
    "    'Gene3': [12.3, 12.8, 18.5, 19.2, 12.0, 12.3],\n",
    "    'Gene4': [9.8, 10.1, 16.1, 15.8, 9.5, 9.8],\n",
    "    'Gene5': [11.2, 11.5, 17.2, 17.8, 11.0, 11.2]\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "df = pd.DataFrame(data)\n",
    "print(\"原始数据:\")\n",
    "print(df)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 数据标准化"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "numeric_data = df[['Gene1', 'Gene2', 'Gene3', 'Gene4', 'Gene5']]\n",
    "sample_names = df['Sample'].values\n",
    "\n",
    "scaler = StandardScaler()\n",
    "scaled_data = scaler.fit_transform(numeric_data)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"标准化后的数据:\")\n",
    "print(scaled_data)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. PCA分析"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "pca = PCA(n_components=2)\n",
    "pca_result = pca.fit_transform(scaled_data)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"PCA结果:\")\n",
    "print(f\"解释方差比: {pca.explained_variance_ratio_}\")\n",
    "print(f\"累积解释方差: {pca.explained_variance_ratio_.cumsum()}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "pca_df = pd.DataFrame(pca_result, columns=['PC1', 'PC2'])\n",
    "pca_df['Sample'] = sample_names\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\nPCA坐标:\")\n",
    "print(pca_df)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 可视化"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 2, figsize=(14, 12))\n",
    "\n",
    "# PCA图\n",
    "axes[0, 0].scatter(pca_df['PC1'], pca_df['PC2'], s=100, alpha=0.7)\n",
    "for i, txt in enumerate(pca_df['Sample']):\n",
    "    axes[0, 0].annotate(txt, (pca_df['PC1'][i], pca_df['PC2'][i]), \n",
    "                         xytext=(5, 5), textcoords='offset points')\n",
    "axes[0, 0].set_xlabel(f'PC1 ({pca.explained_variance_ratio_[0]*100:.2f}%)')\n",
    "axes[0, 0].set_ylabel(f'PC2 ({pca.explained_variance_ratio_[1]*100:.2f}%)')\n",
    "axes[0, 0].set_title('PCA分析')\n",
    "axes[0, 0].grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 层次聚类树状图\n",
    "linkage_matrix = linkage(scaled_data, method='ward')\n",
    "dendrogram(linkage_matrix, labels=sample_names, ax=axes[0, 1], orientation='left')\n",
    "axes[0, 1].set_title('层次聚类树状图')\n",
    "axes[0, 1].set_xlabel('距离')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 热图\n",
    "im = axes[1, 0].imshow(scaled_data, cmap='viridis', aspect='auto')\n",
    "axes[1, 0].set_xticks(range(len(numeric_data.columns)))\n",
    "axes[1, 0].set_xticklabels(numeric_data.columns, rotation=45)\n",
    "axes[1, 0].set_yticks(range(len(sample_names)))\n",
    "axes[1, 0].set_yticklabels(sample_names)\n",
    "axes[1, 0].set_title('热图')\n",
    "axes[1, 0].set_xlabel('基因')\n",
    "axes[1, 0].set_ylabel('样本')\n",
    "plt.colorbar(im, ax=axes[1, 0])\n",
    "\n",
    "# 基因相关性矩阵\n",
    "correlation_matrix = np.corrcoef(scaled_data.T)\n",
    "im2 = axes[1, 1].imshow(correlation_matrix, cmap='coolwarm', vmin=-1, vmax=1)\n",
    "axes[1, 1].set_xticks(range(len(numeric_data.columns)))\n",
    "axes[1, 1].set_xticklabels(numeric_data.columns, rotation=45)\n",
    "axes[1, 1].set_yticks(range(len(numeric_data.columns)))\n",
    "axes[1, 1].set_yticklabels(numeric_data.columns)\n",
    "axes[1, 1].set_title('基因相关性矩阵')\n",
    "plt.colorbar(im2, ax=axes[1, 1])\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Seaborn热图"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))\n",
    "sns.heatmap(scaled_data, \n",
    "            annot=True, \n",
    "            cmap='coolwarm', \n",
    "            xticklabels=numeric_data.columns,\n",
    "            yticklabels=sample_names,\n",
    "            cbar_kws={'label': '标准化值'})\n",
    "plt.title('基因表达热图 (Seaborn)')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('基因')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('样本')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 练习\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习1\n",
    "创建一个箱线图显示每个基因的表达分布\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习2\n",
    "创建一个散点图矩阵，显示所有基因对之间的关系\n",
    "\n",
    "### 练习3\n",
    "尝试不同的聚类方法（single, complete, average），观察树状图的变化"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 在这里编写你的练习代码\n",
    "\n",
    "# 练习1: 箱线图\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))\n",
    "df_melted = df.melt(id_vars=['Sample'], var_name='Gene', value_name='Expression')\n",
    "sns.boxplot(x='Gene', y='Expression', data=df_melted)\n",
    "plt.title('基因表达箱线图')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 练习2: 散点图矩阵\n",
    "sns.pairplot(df[['Gene1", "Gene2", "Gene3", "Gene4", "Gene5"]])\n",
    "plt.suptitle('基因表达散点图矩阵', y=1.02)\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 练习3: 不同聚类方法\n",
    "methods = ['single', 'complete', 'average']\n",
    "fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(18, 5))\n",
    "\n",
    "for i, method in enumerate(methods):\n",
    "    linkage_matrix = linkage(scaled_data, method=method)\n",
    "    dendrogram(linkage_matrix, labels=sample_names, ax=axes[i], orientation='left')\n",
    "    axes[i].set_title(f'层次聚类 ({method})')\n",
    "    axes[i].set_xlabel('距离')\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. 思考题\n",
    "\n",
    "1. PCA和层次聚类有什么不同？\n",
    "2. 为什么在可视化之前要进行数据标准化？\n",
    "3. 热图和相关性矩阵有什么区别？\n",
    "4. 在选择颜色映射时应该考虑哪些因素？"
   ]
  }
 ],
